---
import { OliverParallax } from 'skiper-islands'
---

<section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
    <OliverParallax speed={0.3}>
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/stockholm+scandinavian+interior/600/750"
          alt="Aevo studio in Stockholm"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </OliverParallax>
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold lowercase mb-4 leading-tight">We've been at it since 2007. Still haven't gotten bored.</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#888888] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        What started as a small workshop in Södermalm has grown into a team of twelve designers, engineers, and storytellers. We make watches for people who care about how things are made, not just how they look.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#888888] leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Every material we choose, every supplier we work with, is a decision we stand behind. No shortcuts, no corners cut. Just honest design.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="inline-block border border-[#111] text-[#111] px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium lowercase hover:bg-[#111] hover:text-white transition-colors"
      >
        Read our story
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
